      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You can only affect squares directly exposed to (natural) moonlight. Creatures within the area take 2d6 cold damage. A creature occupying more than one square may be hit more than once.</p>\n\n\n\n",
